<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-numsEnSusDiferentesFormas" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>A, G, and L B and H C and F E and K I, D, and J</p>
<p>Sample response: I know that C and F match because 371 has 3 hundreds, 7 tens, and 1 one, and that’s what I see in the base-ten diagram.</p>
  </solution>


